
CHANGES
=======

0.0.43
------

    * 2006-08-24 (ytekol): More template unicode fixes.
    * 2006-08-24 (ytekol): Template trans fix.
    * 2006-08-24 (ytekol): ``bizcatalog`` fix (Repeat strings).

0.0.42
------

    * 2006-08-19 (ytekol): Correct content-length for unicode strings.
    * 2006-08-19 (ytekol): Template language improved.
    * 2006-08-19 (ytekol): ``biz.catalog`` translation support.
	* 2006-08-12 (ytekol): Default project has favicon.
	* 2006-08-12 (ytekol): ``CachedContent``.

0.0.41
------
    
    * 2006-07-15 (ytekol): ``FunRoot`` and ``MiniRoot`` roots.
    * 2006-07-15 (ytekol): ``TemplateHandler``.
    * 2006-07-15 (ytekol): ``DataGroup`` for obtaining data from any source
      (POST, GET, session, cookies, etc.) that has a dict-like interface.
    * 2006-07-15 (ytekol): ``XmlContent``.
    * 2006-07-15 (ytekol): Better unicode support???
    * 2006-07-15 (ytekol): ``FunApplication``.

0.0.39
------

    * 2006-07-01 (ytekol): Built-in ``Template`` class's ``copy`` method now
      takes *no* parameters and equivalent to the old ``copy(True)``. For the
      old ``copy(False``, there is a distinct method, ``copyall``.

    * 2006-07-01 (ytekol): Built-in ``Template`` class now supports ``open``
      method which accepts both a filename or a file-like object.

0.0.38
------

    * 2006-06-24 (ytekol): Default project unpacker now restores permissions
      (UNIX).

    * 2006-06-24 (ytekol): Documentation is improved.

